These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
House: futuristic, townhouse
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pineapple
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
2. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is the futuristic house##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| House      | futuristic  | townhouse   |
| Food   | pineapple     | avocado   |
| Flower         | orchid | lily |
| Color     | light-blue | grey    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bongani
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, bartender
1. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the bartender##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Cigar          | dunhill     | bongani |
| Sport   | biathlon | basketball  |
| Flower           | azalea         | amaryllis     |
| Job     | journalist   | bartender    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, october
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, montecristo
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Music-Genre    | country     | classical |
| Birthday         | october | march    |
| Flower         | azalea         | orchid        |
| Cigar   | siglo         | montecristo    |

