.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, rose
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, boat
2 different pets are kept: fish, pony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, skiing
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | rose     | aconite |
| Transport          | boat   | motorbike  |
| Pet         | fish | pony     |
| Sport   | surfing  | skiing         |

