.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, turkish
There 2 different types of food: cherry, peas
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening
1. the turkish is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Color    | yellow | apricot    |
| Nationality         | turkish        | polish |
| Food         | cherry          | peas     |
| Hobby   | sudoku        | gardening     |

 